2.02	Dream_of_the_Red_Chamber_(1987_TV_series)	Dream of the Red Chamber (1987 TV series)	Dream of the Red Chamber , released in 1987, was a television series produced by CCTV adapted from the classic Chinese novel Dream of the Red Chamber. It gained enormous popularity with its superb music, cast, and plot adaptation. It was first filmed in Beijing in Mandarin. Then it was translated into Cantonese, Shanghainese, and other languages and aired in the rest of China. It is 36 episodes long.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Traum-der-roten-Kammer.jpg/120px-Traum-der-roten-Kammer.jpg
